Class SaveMenuWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.magicbinder.menu.SaveMenuWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MenuWrapperBase

    public class SaveMenuWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements MenuWrapperBase
    Menu wrapper for save action. To implement a save menu item in your fragment or activity, just make this fragment/activity implement the SaveMenuInterface
